high_descs: Turn around and head towards the sink then turn right and go next to the toilet then turn right
Pick up a bottle of lotion from the toilet tank lid
Turn right then turn right again and go to the sink
Put the lotion bottle on the counter between the two sinks
Turn left and go to the sink on the left side of the counter, then turn right
Get the lotion bottle from the cupboard under the counter
Turn right then turn left to face the lotion bottle that is on the counter
Put the lotion bottle on the counter next to the other one
anns.task_desc: Put two lotion bottles on the counter

high_descs: Turn around and walk around to the left side of the toilet
Pick up the middle pump bottle from the toilet
Turn around and walk up to the counter between the sinks
Put the bottle on the counter between the sinks
Move slightly left then turn back to face the counter
Open the right cabinet below the left sink and remove the pump bottle
Move slightly right then turn back toward the counter
Put the bottle on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put the pump bottles on the bathroom counter

high_descs: Walk around to the other side of the toilet.
Pick up the soap bottle in the middle of the other two.
Turn around and walk to the rightmost sink.
Place the soap bottle on the counter to the left of the sink, parallel with the front sink edge.
Take a step left and face the other sink.
Take the soap bottle out of the bottom right cabinet under the right sink.
Take a step left.
Place the spray bottle on the counter to the left of the first soap bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place two soap bottles on a counter.
